Output demos/vhs/out/03-swarm-dashboard.mp4
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "# Second pane: swarm_watch.py (staged hooks progress)" Enter
Sleep 800ms

Hide
Type "bash demos/vhs/bin/animate-swarm.sh" Enter
Sleep 22s
Show

Type "# Eight leaves complete - coordinator synthesizes" Enter
Sleep 2s